        {
            "+content": "Schwarz, a die-hard FPS gamer, was in the middle of a Virtual Reality Multiple Battlefield match when one wrong step sent him tumbling off the map. He expected \"Game Over\" -- instead, he woke up in a world of swords and sorcery. With no way home and no magic to his name, Schwarz is quickly branded a \"dud\" by the locals... until his modern rifle proves more than a match for spellcraft. <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
